Invocation Name: anxiety relief meditations
des: Anxiety Relief Meditations provides 5 sequential guided meditations to help you transform the way you deal with anxiety. It is recommended to set aside some time every day for some meditation to alleviate stress and clear your mind. To begin your meditation invoke the skill with 'Open Anxiety Relief Meditations' and follow the prompts. If you like this skill and find it to be a useful addition to your mindfulness practice we would really appreciate if you drop us a review! Any suggestions, questions, or bug reports are welcome at support@stokedskills.com. We'd love to hear your feedback so we can continue to improve our products. Enjoy!
